com.android.gis

类 DatasetVector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.android.gis.Dataset
      • com.android.gis.DatasetVector

  • public class DatasetVector
extends Dataset
    矢量数据集
    矢量数据集是数据集的子类，由多个几何对象集合组成。数据包括几何数据和属性数据。

      • GetObjectCount

        public int GetObjectCount()
        获取数据集中数据对象个数
        返回:
        返回数据对象个数
        示例代码:
          DataSource ds = new DataSource();
          DatasetVector dstv = new DatasetVector();
          int nCount = -1;
          if(ds.Open("/sdcard/jingjin/Jingjin.udb")){
              dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDatasetAt(0);
              nCount = dstv.GetObjectCount();
              nCount = dstv.GetFieldCount();
          }

      • CreateField

        public boolean CreateField(FieldInfo fieldInfo)
        创建字段
        参数:
        fieldInfo - 字段描述信息
        返回:
        字段创建成功返回true，否则返回false
        示例代码:
          DataSource ds = new DataSource();
          DatasetVector dstv = new DatasetVector();
          FieldInfo fInfo = new FieldInfo();
          String strName ="";
          boolean bRt = false;
          int nType = -1;
          if(ds.Open("/sdcard/jingjin/Jingjin.udb")){
              dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDataset("点");
              nCount = dstv.GetFieldCount();
              fInfo.fieldName="NewFieldName";
              fInfo.foreignName = "NewField";
              fInfo.type = FieldInfo.FIELDTYPE_TEXT;
              fInfo.size = 256;
              bRt = dstv.CreateField(fInfo);
              nCount = dstv.GetFieldCount();
          }

      • DeleteField

        public boolean DeleteField(java.lang.String name)
        删除字段

          }

      • GetFieldInfoAt

        public FieldInfo GetFieldInfoAt(int nFieldIndex)
        根据字段序号获取字段信息
        参数:
        nFieldIndex - 字段序号
        返回:
        返回字段描述信息
        示例代码:
          DataSource ds = new DataSource();
          DatasetVector dstv = new DatasetVector();
          FieldInfo fInfo = new FieldInfo();
          String strName ="";
          int nType = -1;
          int nCount = -1;
          if(ds.Open("/sdcard/jingjin/Jingjin.udb")){
              dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDataset("点");
              nCount = dstv.GetFieldCount();
              fInfo = dstv.GetFieldInfoAt(7);    //字段属性序号从0开始
              strName = fInfo.fieldName;
              nType = fInfo.type;
          }

      • setFieldInfo

        public boolean setFieldInfo(java.lang.String strName,
                   FieldInfo fieldInfo)
        设置指定名称字段的字段信息
        参数:
        strName - 待设置字段的字段名称
        fieldInfo - 字段信息
        返回:
        设置成功返回true,设置失败返回false
        示例代码:
          DataSource ds = new DataSource();
          DatasetVector dstv = new DatasetVector();
          FieldInfo fInfo = new FieldInfo();
          int nCount = -1;
          String strName = "NAME";
          if(ds.Open("/sdcard/jingjin/Jingjin.udb")){
              dstv = (DatasetVector)ds.GetDataset("点");
              nCount = dstv.GetFieldCount();
              fInfo = dstv.GetFieldInfoAt(15);
              fInfo.foreignName = "newName";
              bRt = dstv.setFieldInfo(strName, fInfo);
          }

      • QueryByID

        public Recordset QueryByID(int[] pIDs)
        根据ID查询数据对象
        参数:
        pIDs - 对象ID数组
        返回:
        返回查询记录集
        备注:
        查询记录集(Recordset)需要调用DatasetVector.ReleaseRecordset()进行释放
        示例代码:
          DataSource datasource = new DataSource();
          datasource = workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0);
          int[] IDs={1,2,3};
          
          DatasetVector datasetvector = new DatasetVector();
          datasetvector = (DatasetVector)datasource.GetDatasetAt(0);
          Recordset recordset = datasetvector.queryByID(IDs);
          int iRSCount = recordset.GetRecordCount();
          datasetvector.ReleaseRecordset(recordset);

      • QueryByGeneral

        public Recordset QueryByGeneral(java.lang.String strSQL)
        根据SQL语句查询数据对象
        参数:

        返回:

          String strSQL = "GVal > 1518";

      • QueryByAround

        public Recordset QueryByAround(Point2D pntCenter,
                      double dDistanceInMeters)
        根据周边范围查询数据对象
        参数:
        pntCenter - 查询中心点
        dDistanceInMeters - 查询半径，单位米
        返回:
        返回查询记录集
        示例代码:
        查询记录集(Recordset)需要调用DatasetVector.ReleaseRecordset()进行释放
        示例代码:
          DataSource datasource = new DataSource();
          datasource = workspace.GetDataSourceAt(0);
          Point2D pntCenter = new Point2D();
          pntCenter.x = 100;
          pntCenter.y = 100;
          
          DatasetVector datasetvector = new DatasetVector();
          datasetvector = (DatasetVector)datasource.GetDatasetAt(0);
          Recordset recordset = datasetvector.QueryByAround(pntCenter,1000);
          int iRSCount = recordset.GetRecordCount();
          datasetvector.ReleaseRecordset(recordset);

      • QueryByDef

        public Recordset QueryByDef(QueryDef queryDef)
        根据复合条件查询数据对象
        参数:
        queryDef - 查询条件
        返回:
        返回查询记录集
        查询记录集(Recordset)需要调用DatasetVector.ReleaseRecordset()进行释放
        示例代码:
          QueryDef qDef = new QueryDef();
          qDef.Type = QueryDef.QT_General;
          qDef.Options = 3;
          qDef.Filter = "ID>101";
          qDef.Sort = "SMID";
          Recordset rs = datasetvector.QueryByDef(qDef);
          int nRSCount = rs.GetRecordCount();
          ......
          datasetvector.ReleaseRecordset(rs);

      • ReleaseRecordset

        public boolean ReleaseRecordset(Recordset hRS)
        释放查询记录集
        参数:
        hRS - 待释放记录集
        返回:
        释放成功返回true，否则返回false
        备注:
